{
  "stem": "1338.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all my classmates came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As usual, it was the requirement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to go to my classmates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, that was the natural exchange.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so that's about all I remember about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the fountain pens, and the watches, and whatever, went with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, for example, a briefcase that I got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I carried it through all-- into the ghetto, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was a nice, leather briefcase, which was very important for a 13-year-old kid, because, in our times-- now, we have gone back now to the ruck sack.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's now become very popular.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But in those day, only you carried that when you were a kid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When you became older, you were going to carry a briefcase.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so at 13, it was-- probably, that was the passage to manhood, more so [LAUGHS] than anything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That why I remember the briefcase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we obviously were very deeply immersed in the Polish culture, on an intellectual level.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, my cousin was already quite well known in the theater in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I-- is there a problem?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have seen-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] as far as meeting people, my father worked with Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With people socially, of course, not that much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, obviously, the Jewish community-- particularly in Lodz, where there was a third of the population was Jewish-- it's its own institution, its own theaters, its own arts, everything had its own on one hand.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the other hand, Jews were very heavily, deeply involved in the Polish cultural life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were contributors.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
